OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776157566
OL,3,CMore than 100 passengers miss flight
OL,4,Cto Manchester after new EU border
OL,5,Cchecks
OL,7,FPassengers were left stranded in Milan
OL,8,Fas new border-control checks caused
OL,9,Fdelays at Linate Airport
OL,11,FMore than 100 passengers were left
OL,12,Fstranded in Milan after an EasyJet
OL,13,Fflight to Manchester was delayed
OL,14,Ftaking off due to long queues at
OL,15,Fpassport control.
OL,17,FPassengers were due to depart on
OL,18,FSunday but faced queues of up to three
OL,19,Fhours at Milan's Linate airport
OL,20,Fbecause of new border control checks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776157566
OL,3,CMore than 100 passengers miss flight
OL,4,Cto Manchester after new EU border
OL,5,Cchecks
OL,7,FThe airline held the flight for nearly
OL,8,Fan hour to allow passengers extra
OL,9,Ftime, but eventually had to depart due
OL,10,Fto crew members reaching their safety-
OL,11,Fregulated operating hours. A total of
OL,12,F122 passengers did not make the flight.
OL,14,FEasyjet said it was trying to support
OL,15,Fpassengers but that the situation was
OL,16,F"outside of our control". Customers
OL,17,Fwho missed the flight have been
OL,18,Foffered a free flight transfer,
OL,19,Faccording to the airline.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776157566
OL,3,CMore than 100 passengers miss flight
OL,4,Cto Manchester after new EU border
OL,5,Cchecks
OL,7,FIt comes after the European Union
OL,8,Fimplemented new border control checks,
OL,9,Fmeaning travellers have to register
OL,10,Ftheir biometric details.
OL,12,FEmily Benn told Good Morning Britain
OL,13,F(GMB): "We got to the airport with
OL,14,Fthree hours to spare yesterday, the
OL,15,Fgate came up, we went straight to the
OL,16,Fgate, we were queuing for two and a
OL,17,Fhalf hours, and then a guy came
OL,18,Fthrough and said your flight's gone.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776157566
OL,3,CMore than 100 passengers miss flight
OL,4,Cto Manchester after new EU border
OL,5,Cchecks
OL,7,F"We've had no communication with
OL,8,FEasyJet themselves, and we've
OL,9,Fbasically managed to book a flight to
OL,10,FGatwick tonight."
OL,12,FPassengers Emily and Jessica turned up
OL,13,Fwith three hours to spare but were
OL,14,Fstill unable to board their flight to
OL,15,FManchester.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
