OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776157566
OL,3,CMore than 100 passengers miss flight
OL,4,Cto Manchester after new EU border
OL,5,Cchecks
OL,7,FThe new Entry/Exit system was
OL,8,Fimplemented across EU airports and
OL,9,Fports last week, meaning British
OL,10,Ftravellers are no longer required to
OL,11,Fhave their passports stamped. Instead,
OL,12,Fa digital biometric system has been
OL,13,Fintroduced.
OL,15,FUntil now, many airports were
OL,16,Feffectively running a double system,
OL,17,Fwith both passport stamps being taken
OL,18,Fand the new biometric digital EES
OL,19,F(Entry/Exit system) also being carried
OL,20,Fout.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776157566
OL,3,CMore than 100 passengers miss flight
OL,4,Cto Manchester after new EU border
OL,5,Cchecks
OL,7,FTravel expert, Simon Calder, has
OL,8,Fwarned that the delays in Milan could
OL,9,Fbe a sign of what is to come.
OL,11,F"The fear is that things could get
OL,12,Fworse before they get better. We
OL,13,Freally need urgent action from the
OL,14,FEuropean Union, and the British
OL,15,Fgovernment should really be leading
OL,16,Fthat campaign," he told GMB.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
