FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776157566
OL,3,CMore than 100 passengers miss flight
OL,4,Cto Manchester after new EU border
OL,5,Cchecks
OL,7,FIn a statement to ITV News, EasyJet
OL,8,Fsaid: "Due to delays in EES processing
OL,9,Fby border authorities, some passengers
OL,10,Fdeparting from Milan Linate yesterday
OL,11,Fexperienced very long waiting times at
OL,12,Fpassport control.
OL,14,F"We held flight EJU5420 from Milan to
OL,15,FManchester for nearly an hour to give
OL,16,Fpassengers extra time, but it had to
OL,17,Fthen depart due to crew reaching their
OL,18,Fsafety-regulated operating hours.
OL,19,FCustomers who missed the flight have
OL,20,Fbeen offered a free flight transfer. "
OL,26,@|D@fOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776157566
OL,3,CMore than 100 passengers miss flight
OL,4,Cto Manchester after new EU border
OL,5,Cchecks
OL,7,F"We continue to urge border
OL,8,Fauthorities to ensure they make full
OL,9,Fand effective use of the permitted
OL,10,Fflexibilities for as long as needed
OL,11,Fwhile EES is implemented, to avoid
OL,12,Fthese unacceptable border delays for
OL,13,Four customers.
OL,15,F"While this is outside of our control,
OL,16,Fwe are sorry for any inconvenience
OL,17,Fcaused."
OL,19,FITV News has contacted Milan's Linate
OL,20,FAirport for comment.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
