OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776157566
OL,3,CMore than 100 passengers miss flight
OL,4,Cto Manchester after new EU border
OL,5,Cchecks
OL,7,FWhat is the EU-entry system?
OL,9,FNon-EU nationals wishing to enter the
OL,10,FSchengen area will now go through
OL,11,Fbiometric checks instead of getting a
OL,12,Fpassport stamp when entering the area.
OL,14,FThese checks will involve face scans
OL,15,Fand fingerprint recording. Children
OL,16,Funder the age of 12 will not need to
OL,17,Fhave their fingerprints scanned.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
