SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776157566
OL,3,CMore than 100 passengers miss flight
OL,4,Cto Manchester after new EU border
OL,5,Cchecks
OL,7,FTravellers will also go through the
OL,8,Fsame check when leaving the area,
OL,9,Fmeaning countries can track when
OL,10,Fvisitors overstay.
OL,12,FFull list of countries using the EES
OL,13,Fsystem:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
