OL,3,CMore than 100 passengers miss flight
OL,4,Cto Manchester after new EU border
OL,5,Cchecks
OL,7,FAustria, Belgium, Bulgaria, Croatia,
OL,8,FCzech Republic, Denmark, Estonia,
OL,9,FFinland, France, Germany, Greece,
OL,10,FHungary, Iceland, Italy, Latvia,
OL,11,FLiechtenstein, Lithuania, Luxembourg,
OL,12,FMalta, Netherlands, Norway, Poland,
OL,13,FPortugal, Romania, Slovakia, Slovenia,
OL,14,FSpain, Sweden, and Switzerland.
OL,16,FIreland and Cyprus are not within the
OL,17,FSchengen area, and therefore, EES is
OL,18,Fnot applicable when travelling to
OL,19,Feither of these countries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
